org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.query.constraints

Class BasicQueryByClass

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.query.constraints.BasicQuery
      • org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.query.constraints.BasicQueryByClass
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Persistable, QueryConstraints
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ExplicitSpatialQuery, ExplicitTemporalQuery

    public class BasicQueryByClass
extends BasicQuery
    The Basic Query class represent a hyper-cube(s) query across all dimensions that match the Constraints passed into the constructor

    NOTE: query to an index that requires a constraint and the constraint is missing within the query equates to an unconstrained index scan. The query filter is still applied.
